This is a '''list of maritime boundary treaties'''. [[Maritime boundary]] treaties are [[treaty|treaties]] that [[Boundary delimitation|establish]] a specified ocean or sea [[border|boundary]] between two or more countries or territories. These are also called '''maritime boundary agreements''', '''maritime delimitation treaties''', or '''maritime delimitation agreements'''.

